programme.title: Drama On 2 – Hanna Raudhah Ep11
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Hanna, gadis yang dibuang keluarganya setelah dia mengandung anak luar nikah kerana dirogol. Akibat bosan kerana kedua ibubapanya sering sibuk bekerja, Hanna secara diam-diam berhibur dan bersosial dengan kawan-kawannya. Akibat lalai, Hanna telah dirogol dan mengandung. Mama tirinya, Datin Kamila telah menghalaunya setelah mengetahui hal itu. Hanna membawa diri tanpa tujuan kerana terlampau letih Hanna pengsan dan kebetulan dibantu oleh Pak Hadi dan Mak Siah.

programme.title: Lavender On 2 – Lawless Love Ep9
programme.desc: Kisah cinta 2 darjat antara Davut yang bekerja sebagai pekerja di lombong arang batu dan Gulfem yang merupakan anak kepada pemilik lombong tersebut. Davut, seorang anak muda yang hidup sederhana tinggal dengan adik-beradik dan ibu bapanya. Dia bekerja sebagai buruh di sebuah lombong arang batu bersama bapa dan adik-adik lelakinya. Dia seorang yang berani dan amat bencikan ketidakadilan. Suatu hari, berlaku tragedi di lombong arang batu akibat pengabaian oleh pemilik lombong dan tragedi itu membuatkan ramai pekerja terbunuh termasuk bapa Davut. Maka bermulalah perjuangan Davut menentang pemilik lombong yang tamak dan kejam terhadap pekerja-pekerjanya.

programme.title: Tanya Hassan S2 Ep13
programme.desc: Dalam episod ini, seorang penonton Tanya Hassan bertanya mengenai seorang majikan meminta wang dari setiap pekerjanya untuk simpanan dan menjanjikan ia akan bertambah dalam masa setahun. Adakah itu riba? Ustaz Hassan menyentuh isu ini. Majikan tidak boleh memaksa sekiranya pekerja tidak mahu memberinya wang. Selain itu juga, jika majikan menjanjikan untuk menaikkan ke 2 atau 3 kali ganda, maka ia tidak dibenarkan dalam islam. Soalan kedua ditanya boleh atau tidak islam menjual biawak dan ular kepada mereka yang bukan islam atas tujuan untuk memakannya.

programme.title: Menantu Tok Sintok Ep6

Bacaan solat mereka diperbetulkan. Selama ini mereka mengaku tak pandai baca Quran dan tak pandai baca jawi. Bacaan solat mereka pun mereka hafal dalam jawi. Tok Sintok meninggalkan mereka berdua malam itu di masjid. Mereka takut. Tok sintok jelaskan rumah Allah kenapa nak takut tidur?

programme.desc: Tanti menyamar dengan memakai wig dan topeng dan mencelakai Riri, untungnya Emak segera datang dan menyelamatkan Riri. programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep01
programme.desc: Meskipun Farah sedang menunggu saat diijabkabulkan, namun dia masih dalam dilema untuk menjadi isteri Lukman. Dia masih keliru dengan keputusannya; antara amanah arwah Sarah dengan keikhlasannya menerima abang iparnya sebagai suami. Baik Lukman mahupun Farah, kedua-duanya terpaksa maniskan wajah di majlis pernikahan mereka demi menjaga hati Zahin dan kedua-dua orang tua. Di sebalik kegembiraan, ada hati yang tercarik luka dengan pernikahan mereka. Lantaran terlalu kecewa, Myra sanggup bertindak di luar kawalan hingga menyebabkannya kemalangan dan koma. Joshua muncul untuk membantu Myra lalu membawanya ke hospital. Lukman pula resah kerana tidak dapat menjejak Myra setelah Myra hilang begitu sahaja ketika majlis pernikahannya berlangsung. Farah kecewa apabila Lukman berterus terang yang dia takkan menyentuh Farah kerana dia hanya setia dan cintakan arwah isterinya, Sarah

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep10
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza berkenalan melalui sistem SMS. Masing-masing tidak ada clue tentang latar belakang atau paras rupa, sekadar bermain kata-kata di skrin telefon bimbit dan laptop sahaja. Pada asalnya mereka berkawan secara suka-suka, namun melalui suara dan kata-kata, maka berkuntum rasa cinta, maka diaturkan pula pertemuan di Kuantan yang akhirnya memekarkan perasaan dua hati dan dua jiwa. Malangnya, sejak dulu lagi Rasya mempunyai penyakit paranoia, sangat bimbang kalau dia ditinggalkan. Dia sentiasa sangsi dengan keikhlasan hati Reeza. Apatah lagi Reeza, lelaki urban yang dilabel sebagai kaki flirt, mencurigakan Rasya si gadis kacukan (Melayu-Arab) yang kelihatan sofistikated dari segi fizikalnya, namun mempunyai semangat kampung yang agak tinggi (kerana pernah dibesarkan di Kampung Ijok). Atuk dan opah Rasya di Kampung Ijok pula, sudah lama pasang angan-angan untuk satukan Rasya dengan Fahmi, dua pupu dan rakan sepermainan. Banyak nostalgia lama yang menjadi kenangan bersama Fahmi yang kini merupakan seorang majistret, namun hati Rasya sudah dimilik Reeza seorang arkitek di kota KL. Perasaan paranoid yang menghantui jiwanya, membuatkan Rasya dan Reeza sentiasa bermain tarik-tarik tali. Di suatu sudut, Rasya sangat senang dengan karakter Reeza yang lasak dan aktif, romantis dan budiman. Namun kerana terlalu takut ditinggalkan seperti mana yang pernah terjadi pada diri ketika dia kanak-kanak, Rasya mengizinkan lalu memudahkan peranan Adri (teman Reeza) merasuk fikirannya dan akhirnya Rasya tinggalkan Reeza untuk berkahwin dengan Fahmi. Setahun berlalu, Reeza gundah gulana, lalu terpaksa dirawat di Janda Baik, Pahang. Di sana seraya mendapat rawatan untuk mengubat kesakitan jiwa raga, dia dihampiri Hilda, anak gadis teman ibu bapa Reeza. Maka berpakat-pakatlah dua keluarga untuk menyatukan Reeza dan Hilda. Reeza dan Hilda bertunang. Setelah pulih, Reeza kembali aktif menjalankan tugasnya dan dia telah ke Dubai untuk bertemu klien.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep20
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila bersama Nizam yang bersetuju berlakon sebagai suami yang biasa. Sheila memperkenalkan Nizam kepada ibunya yang masih berada di katil hospital. Ibu Sheila terima dengan seadanya. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan terus mesra membuatkan Nizam mencemburui. Cemburu Nizam terus menebal apabila Hani mengakui dia telah mengandung kepada keluarganya, walau pun itu satu helah dia bersama Mizan. Mempercayai itu, Nizam telah menghubungi Suraya dan mengugutnya lagi. Dia meminta Suraya melakukan sesuatu asalkan kandungan Hani gugur. Bertindak dari itu, Suraya bertemu Hani dan Mizan yang baru dirawat tangannya. Mizan diminta Hani berada di dalam kereta, semasa inilah sempat Suraya menyiku perut Hani. Mizan yang keluar membantu dihentak dengan beg tangannya berisi batu. Mizan menerima rawatan pesakit luar. Ketika ibu bapa mereka melawat, Nizam turut serta tetapi hanya berpura-pura. Kesempatan itu, Nizam cuba mendekati Hani mendesak dan memujuknya. Hani tetap menolak sambil bertegas dia amat mencintai Mizan. Suraya kini bimbang dia diburu polis. Kebetulan Dato Fuad yang menyimpannya datang. Suraya terus mengadu membuatkan Dato Fuad mengaturkan orang-orangnya untuk menghalang Nizam mengugut Suraya dan memberi ribuan ringgit. Hubungan Nizam dengan Sheila masih dingin dan Nizam mengulangi dia tetap memperisterikan Hani. Setelah berfikir sebak mungkin, Mizan menghubungi ibu dan bapanya memaklumkan Hani keguguran dan tiada masalah.

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep04
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Siqma, Sherry Ibrahim, Zeppo Youngsterz dan juga kugiran Motherwit.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep28
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.desc: Pertemuan kali pertama antara Malvin Khoo dan Atita Harris telah menimbulkan kemarahan Malvin. Sikap Atita yang suka menjawab menimbulkan rasa tidak puas hati Malvin terhadap tea lady yang bekerja di tingkat VIP pejabatnya. Malvin merasakan Atita melakukan kerja sambil lewa. Namun setelah selalu bertikam lidah, Malvin mendapati Atita adalah seorang gadis yang bijak. Namun, Perbezaan agama yang dianuti menjadi halangan besar buat mereka meneruskan hubungan walaupun Malvin adalah seorang Atheist. Madam Khoo sama sekali tidak mahu melepaskan Malvin kepada Atita. Malvin serba salah. Antara ibu dan kekasih, yang mana patut didahulukan? Mempertahankan cintanya atau terus menjadi anak yang patuh?

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep17
programme.desc: Haris mengantarkan Riri pulang ke rumahnya. Sinta bahagia karena Riri mau pulang. Arya masih cemberut, tapi Sinta menuntun Riri ke dalam kamarnya. Arya masih kesal, tapi dia tahu. Andi berusaha untuk lebih sehat dan bangkit dari kursi roda. Andi bersemangat karena dia akan segera menikah dengan Riri. Tapi Andi kepikiran janjinya terhadap Arya. programme.title: Rock Bro
programme.desc: Rock Bro! diceritakan melalui naratif Jijoe, kemuncak pencapaian mereka apabila menjadi finalis Anugerah Juara Lagu, namun era rock mula meniti fasa kejatuhan dengan kemasukan aliran muzik rap dan hip-hop pada awal 90-an. Amy Mat Piah meninggalkan jawatan sebagai pengurus kumpulan Rimba Bara kerana keinginanya yang terlalu kuat untuk menjadi penyanyi Rock. Namun begitu,o kumpulan Rimba Bara tetap meneruskan perjuangan musik mereka..Rimba Bara menerima seorang pembantu bernama Dio. Pada ketika ini jemputan untuk membuat persembahan mula berkurang sehingga memaksa mereka melakukan kerja sambilan bagi menyara hidup, selain mengambil tawaran gig di tapak ekspo tani. Disaat ini hati Zul Kapan mula berbolak balik dek kerana kecewa dengan perjalanan musik kumpulan mereka. Pada ketika ini juga prestasi Black mula terjejas kerana penyakit misteri. Zul yang sudah mula bosan mengambil keputusan untuk meninggalkan dunia muzik dan melibatkan diri dengan aktiviti agama.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep10
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza berkenalan melalui sistem SMS. Masing-masing tidak ada clue tentang latar belakang atau paras rupa, sekadar bermain kata-kata di skrin telefon bimbit dan laptop sahaja. Pada asalnya mereka berkawan secara suka-suka, namun melalui suara dan kata-kata, maka berkuntum rasa cinta, maka diaturkan pula pertemuan di Kuantan yang akhirnya memekarkan perasaan dua hati dan dua jiwa. Malangnya, sejak dulu lagi Rasya mempunyai penyakit paranoia, sangat bimbang kalau dia ditinggalkan. Dia sentiasa sangsi dengan keikhlasan hati Reeza. Apatah lagi Reeza, lelaki urban yang dilabel sebagai kaki flirt, mencurigakan Rasya si gadis kacukan (Melayu-Arab) yang kelihatan sofistikated dari segi fizikalnya, namun mempunyai semangat kampung yang agak tinggi (kerana pernah dibesarkan di Kampung Ijok). Atuk dan opah Rasya di Kampung Ijok pula, sudah lama pasang angan-angan untuk satukan Rasya dengan Fahmi, dua pupu dan rakan sepermainan. Banyak nostalgia lama yang menjadi kenangan bersama Fahmi yang kini merupakan seorang majistret, namun hati Rasya sudah dimilik Reeza seorang arkitek di kota KL. Perasaan paranoid yang menghantui jiwanya, membuatkan Rasya dan Reeza sentiasa bermain tarik-tarik tali. Di suatu sudut, Rasya sangat senang dengan karakter Reeza yang lasak dan aktif, romantis dan budiman. Namun kerana terlalu takut ditinggalkan seperti mana yang pernah terjadi pada diri ketika dia kanak-kanak, Rasya mengizinkan lalu memudahkan peranan Adri (teman Reeza) merasuk fikirannya dan akhirnya Rasya tinggalkan Reeza untuk berkahwin dengan Fahmi. Setahun berlalu, Reeza gundah gulana, lalu terpaksa dirawat di Janda Baik, Pahang. Di sana seraya mendapat rawatan untuk mengubat kesakitan jiwa raga, dia dihampiri Hilda, anak gadis teman ibu bapa Reeza. Maka berpakat-pakatlah dua keluarga untuk menyatukan Reeza dan Hilda. Reeza dan Hilda bertunang. Setelah pulih, Reeza kembali aktif menjalankan tugasnya dan dia telah ke Dubai untuk bertemu klien.

programme.title: Terbaik Dari Jalanan S1 Ep08
programme.desc: Ikuti Suffren dan Banni dalam jelajah mereka menikmati makanan-makanan terbaik dari gerai, warung dan kedai kaki lima. Kali ini, mereka akan pergi ke Nasi Lemak Maklong, 20 Laman Cafe, Babypancake Bergegau dan DCabin Satay Kajang.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep02
programme.desc: Farah masih terkilan dengan kata-kata Lukman pada malam pertama pernikahan mereka apatah lagi Lukman menyebut nama Myra dalam tidurnya. Farah berasa kurang senang apabila Lukman berpura-pura romantis dengannya di depan famili. Budi terkejut apabila Lukman datang ke pejabat sehari selepas bernikah seakan-akan mahu mengelak daripada Farah. Lukman terkejut setelah menerima surat perletakan jawatan Myra yang ditinggalkan di atas meja. Papa menegur Lukman yang berperangai seperti orang bujang dan balik lewat meskipun sudah berkahwin. Akibat terasa dengan teguran Papa, Lukman bertindak mengajak Farah balik ke rumahnya. Farah cuba menyesuaikan diri dengan keadaan rumah Lukman yang bersepah dan seakan tidak terurus selepas kematian Sarah. Lukman cemburu dan mula syak wasangka apabila melihat Farah bersama Nazim di kafe.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S13 Ep07
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Chef Naem, tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat.

programme.title: K-Love Ep10
programme.desc: Tish mengaku kepada Jay yang dia menyukainya sejak zaman kanak-kanak, Val sangat memerlukan gaun untuk Majlis Tari-Menari Tatler manakala Shiela tertanya-tanya kenapa David berada dalam mood yang tak baik dengannya.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S16 Ep10
programme.desc: Dengan bajet RM10, Chef Naem, tukang masak Dapur Bujang akan menyediakan dua jenis hidangan masakan harian yang senang, sedap dan sihat.

programme.title: Lie After Lie Ep13
programme.desc: Kim Ho Ran memberikan laporan ujian DNA kepada Se Mi dan Se Mi diserahkan kepada Ji Min. Ji Min bertanya kepada Eun Su sama ada dia benar-benar ibu kandung Woo Joo. Eun Su mengaku bahawa memang benar dia mendekatinya dan Woo Joo dengan motif tersembunyi. Kecewa, Ji Min memberitahunya dia tidak mahu berjumpa dengannya lagi.

programme.title: Japanizi Going Going Gong Ep15
programme.desc: Japanizi Going Going Gong ialah pertunjukan permainan fizikal kanak-kanak Kanada dengan motif Jepun di mana peserta bersaing dengan rakan sepasukan menentang pasukan lain semasa mereka menangani halangan dan cabaran untuk menguji keupayaan mental, kekuatan, ketahanan dan kepintaran mereka.

programme.title: #ustaz masak S3 Ep02
programme.desc: Dalam rancangan ini dalam setiap episod Cef Fendi dan Ustaz Jemputan yang berlainan di setiap episode akan mengembara ke destinasi seperti ladang dan tempat perusahaan makanan yang berasaskan bahan masakan yang sering digunakan untuk memasak. Berkonsepkan outdoor cooking, rancangan ini membawakan resepi masakan yang menarik dan enak yang akan dimasak bersama Fendi dan Ustaz jemputan. Rancangan ini bercorak Santai namun tetap menyelitkan informasi berguna seperti petua-petua yang dilupakan.

programme.title: Hanya Tuhan Yang Tahu
programme.desc: Ramlan dan Maria membawa anak perempuannya, Shazlin untuk tinggal bersama mereka demi keselamatan Shazlin. Dia telah dipukul oleh Along kerana suaminya, Iskandar berhutang. Shazlin hanya diam tetapi tertekan dengan permasalahan itu. Ramlan pula bersimpati pada Iskandar dan ingin membantunya menyelesaikan hutang Iskandar dengan Along. Tetapi dalam masa yang sama, Ramlan memasang perangkap adakah benar Iskandar berhutang dengan Along.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep01
programme.desc: Meskipun Farah sedang menunggu saat diijabkabulkan, namun dia masih dalam dilema untuk menjadi isteri Lukman. Dia masih keliru dengan keputusannya; antara amanah arwah Sarah dengan keikhlasannya menerima abang iparnya sebagai suami. Baik Lukman mahupun Farah, kedua-duanya terpaksa maniskan wajah di majlis pernikahan mereka demi menjaga hati Zahin dan kedua-dua orang tua. Di sebalik kegembiraan, ada hati yang tercarik luka dengan pernikahan mereka. Lantaran terlalu kecewa, Myra sanggup bertindak di luar kawalan hingga menyebabkannya kemalangan dan koma. Joshua muncul untuk membantu Myra lalu membawanya ke hospital. Lukman pula resah kerana tidak dapat menjejak Myra setelah Myra hilang begitu sahaja ketika majlis pernikahannya berlangsung. Farah kecewa apabila Lukman berterus terang yang dia takkan menyentuh Farah kerana dia hanya setia dan cintakan arwah isterinya, Sarah

programme.title: Sayang Achu Ketat-Ketat
programme.desc: Sepasang suami isteri Irfan Zaqri dan Auliyah Insyirah sudah 5 tahun berkahwin dan belum memilki anak.Mereka bercadang untuk berpisah. Satu hari mereka di amanahkan untuk menjaga 2 orang anak arwah kakak Irfan. Jadikah rancangan mereka untuk berpisah?

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.title: Ronda-Ronda S1 Ep06
programme.desc: Sebuah rancangan yang memaparkan 2 orang pencinta dunia motosikal menunggang motosikal dan ronda-ronda di sekitar untuk mencari dan membongkar tempat-tempat menarik dan tersembunyi, dan juga tempat-tempat makan yang popular dan sedap. Episod kali ini menampilkan lokasi-lokasi menarik dan tempat makan yang wajib anda singgah di Seri Kembangan.

programme.title: Jalan-Jalan Makan Angin (2019) Ep07
programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. Antaranya ialah: 1. Sarang By The Brook, K. Kubu Bharu : -Konsep kontena dikelilingi hutan alam semulajadi, kemudahan asas termasuk penghawa dingin dan tempat tidur. -Bilik serendah RM180/ malam. -Aktiviti : Jungle tracking, mandi sungai. 2. Dusun Bonda, Batang Kali : -Konsep berkhemah dikelilingi kolam dan alam semulajadi, suasana kampung, penghawa dingin, private garden, tandas peribadi -Bilik studio : tandas persendirian, dapur, sungai, -Aktiviti : BBQ, makan malam di atas bumbung dengan suasana romantik, sarapan pagi di tepi sungai, melihat ladang madu kelulut. -Bilik serendah RM350/ malam.

programme.title: Lawak Sentral S4 Ep03
programme.desc: Lawak Sental adalah kompilasi sketsa sketsa lawak santai pendek yang pasti membuat anda gelak ketawa dan terhibur.

programme.title: Jom Fesyen S4 Ep06
programme.desc: Jom Fesyen merupakan program berteraskan kepada pamakaian wanita Muslimah. Jom Fesyen membawa penonton mengenali, menyaksikan kreativiti pereka tempatan yang menghasilkan busana Muslimah di pasaran.

programme.title: Terbaik Dari Jalanan S1 Ep04
programme.desc: Ikuti Suffren dan Banni dalam jelajah mereka menikmati makanan-makanan terbaik dari gerai, warung dan kedai kaki lima. Kali ini, mereka akan pergi ke Nasi Lemak Maklong, 20 Laman Cafe, Babypancake Bergegau dan DCabin Satay Kajang.

programme.title: Saat Hati Telah Memilih Ep27
programme.desc: Tanti dibawa ke rumah sakit oleh Mak Waroh karena dia demam dan menggigil. Karin melihat Haris dan berusaha menghampirinya dengan kursi roda namun Tanti melihatnya dan menahan Karin. Tanti kemudian mencelakai Karin namun Karin berhasil ditolong oleh Mak Waroh. Riri kaget melihat Karin di rumahnya dan berlari memanggil Mak Waroh ketakutan namun Riri terpeleset. Riri pingsan dan dibawa ke rumah sakit hingga akhirnya Riri melahirkan prematur dan kondisinya kritis. Arya marah besar ke Andi masalah pekerjaan dan membuat jantung Andi kumat hingga koma. Arya merasa bersalah dan kepikiran Iren yang akan semakin membencinya.

programme.title: Demi Hati Arjuna
programme.desc: Alia disahkan menghidap penyakit hati Cirrhosis. Alia teringat masa silamnya memang liar. Bagi merawat penyakitnya, dia disaran melakukan transplan. Namun. Alia yang sebatang kara sukar untuk dia mendapatkan penderma. Dia kemudian teringat akan Arjuna, anak yang dia lahirkan 12 tahun dahulu bersama Zafran. Zafran tidak mahu bertanggungjawab. Anak itu diserahkan kepada orang lain selepas dinamakan sebagai Arjuna.

programme.title: K-Love Ep02
programme.desc: Berikutan susulan lamarannya yang tergesa-gesa, Tish menavigasi cara mengendalikan perjumpaan keluarga yang akan datang tanpa Raffy di sisinya. Sheila ingin meyakinkan anak perempuannya Anya bahawa dia adalah subjek yang layak untuk tugasan seorang gadis yang cool. Val sebaliknya bergelut untuk meyakinkan ibunya bahawa dia sihat, dan tidak mengalami sebarang masalah kewangan.

programme.title: Puteri Gunung Ledang S1 Ep29
programme.desc: Natasya hanya berkelulusan SPM tetapi bijak, agak lasak dan adakala lebih bersifat seperti lelaki. Namun sesekali dia berdandan dan bersolek, pastinya kebanyakan pemuda kampung akan terpikat dengan kecantikan yang dimiliki oleh Natasya dan memanggilnya Puteri Gunung Ledang. Natasya berimpian menjadi model terkenal. Setiap kali mencuba nasib, dia gagal dan akhirnya bekerja sebagai kerani di sebuah agensi peragaan sahaja. Nasibnya berubah apabila dia menjadi duta produk kecantikan secara tidak sengaja. Ramai yang mula jatuh hati dan terpikat pada kecantikan Natasya termasuklah majikannya Rayyan. Rayyan seorang lelaki yang kacak tetapi bersikap kaki perempuan. Mereka berkenalan secara lebih dekat tetapi Natasya meletakkan tujuh syarat untuk membuktikan cintanya

programme.title: Bakar S3 Ep15
programme.desc: Pada kali ini, Bakar akan membakar resipi resipi yang sudah tentunya menarik dan enak.

programme.title: Resepi Moyang S8 Ep08
programme.desc: Resepi Moyang merupakan sebuah rancangan memasak yang mengetengahkan masakan tradisional dari serata Malaysia dan juga luar negara. Dalam episod ini, hos akan belajar memasak masakan Vietnam iaitu Banh Xeo dan Karipap Gulung. Dihoskan oleh Emilia Han.

programme.desc: Sebuah rumah, di mana telah berlaku pembunuhan keluarga, yang terdiri daripada seorang suami, isteri dan anak lelaki mereka. Sejak itu, rumah tersebut dikenali sebagai Rumah Berhantu Pondok Indah, kerana setiap penghuni baru yang menghuni rumah tersebut sentiasa digeruni oleh roh/hantu yang menghuni rumah tersebut. Beberapa tahun kemudian, sebuah keluarga baru menduduki rumah itu, jadi perkara yang sama berlaku lagi. Mereka digeruni oleh hantu rumah. Bolehkah mereka menyelamatkan diri daripada ketakutan hantu rumah atau dibunuh seorang demi seorang?

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Melati, Golok, Sigit dan Ari bersiap sedia untuk melawan Kusno. Sara memasuki losmen mencari Fadil tetapi akhirnya terperangkap di salah satu bilik. Di sana, dia mendapati Fadil terperangkap dalam perigi dari episod 4. Diserang oleh roh rumah, Sara cuba menyelamatkan Fadil dan akhirnya mengorbankan dirinya dalam proses itu. Melati meyakinkan arwah rumah untuk berpihak kepadanya dalam perjuangannya menentang Kusno. Kusno dan Pemburu menyerang Losmen Melati. Sigit berbaik semula dengan Ari atas kengerian masa lalunya dan menentang ayahnya untuk kebaikan. Kini keluar dari perigi, Fadil cuba keluar dari rumah tetapi tersedut untuk melawan Kusno. Berjuang melawan Kusno sendiri, Fadil berada di ambang kematian apabila Kusno menggigitnya, membiarkan kutukan memasuki sistemnya. Apabila semua kelihatan hilang untuk Melati, dia mendedahkan senjata rahsianya - Watih, yang Kusno dipercayai telah mati, kembali untuk memberikan pukulan maut terakhir, akhirnya mengalahkan Kusno sekali dan untuk selama-lamanya. Namun apabila hari baru menjelma, Fadil muncul semula, tetapi semuanya tidak seperti yang disangka. Mata Fadil menjadi hitam, membayangkan kisah Losmen Melati belum berakhir.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep206
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep9
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep285286
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep497
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: My Hero, My Daddy (M) Ep1213
programme.desc: A fathers love for his daughters landed Jinfa Huang in battles against other men right within his family, as he found himself in conflict with his sons-in-law. His 3 daughters each possessed a distinct personality but were similarly headstrong and in romantic relationships that caused their fathers brows to crease. Tianlan, his eldest, was in love with Minglu Xu, Jinfas superior who never missed an opportunity to make life difficult for him; Tianhong, his second daughter, was drifting apart from him because of her husband; meanwhile, his youngest girl was challenging the taboo of a campus romance. How would Jinfa emerge victor in this fight to protect the 3 loves of his life?

programme.title: Turns We Take
programme.desc: A spicy hot pot restaurant in Northeast China serves different types of customers every day. Amongst them are a sweet young couple, two wayward young men and a taxi driver. Despite being complete strangers to each other, their lives are intertwined by a traffic accident

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: My Country, My Parents
programme.desc: Set in 4 different eras in China, the 4-part anthology about home and country is directed by Wu Jing, Zhang Zi Yi, Xu Zheng and Shen Teng, who also star in their own story. The movie depicts how the fathers forge ahead through the struggle of times, defending strong family ties and passing on the fighting spirit through generations.

programme.title: The White Storm 2: Drug Lords
programme.desc: In this epic action-thriller starring Andy Lau and Louis Koo, the two award-winning best actors star on opposing sides of a drug war. As a bounty of $100 million Hong Kong dollars is made to hunt down the biggest drug dealer in the city, Hong Kong becomes the battleground for the fight between good and evil.

programme.title: Flashover
programme.desc: This is based on a true story. A sudden earthquake hits the gas pipes in an industrial park, triggering massive explosions and engulfing the neighboring area in flames. When the Fire Rescue Force reaches the scene, firefighters must fight against the flames and time, as they commit to safeguard lives with their own.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs
programme.desc: Yan is a police mole in the triad and joined them before he graduated from the police academy, while Ming is a triad mole in the police since young. Leading parallel lives, both men feel increasingly trapped in their false surroundings, and a series of cat-and-mouse chases ensue as both the triad and the police compete to uncover the others mole.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say yes?

programme.title: Mama's Affair
programme.desc: Former talent manager Mei Fung stays home to take care of her husband and son after retirement. She decides to re-enter the entertainment business to find her value in life, and successfully transforms a local restaurant delivery boy, Fong Ching, into a young pop idol. This makes her teenage son, Jonathan, intensely jealous of Fong Ching.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriends wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: July Rhapsody
programme.desc: A 40-year-old high school teacher is in midlife crisis, his marriage is on the rocks and he is involved in a taboo romance with a female student who has a crush on him. Meanwhile, his wife is off to care for her dying ex-lover who shares a complicated history with the couple...

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: God of Gambler's Return
programme.desc: The God of Gamblers, Gao Jin, quits gambling and live a quiet life with his wife. However, a Taiwanese crime boss wants to become the new God of Gamblers and get rid of him, so he kills Gao Jins pregnant wife to force him to the casino table. Gao Jin is indignant and vows to fight the crime boss to avenge his wifes death.

programme.title: Defying Chase
programme.desc: A stunt man finds himself accidentally caught in an international criminal operation involving culture relics hustling and has to fight them for his life. He vows to singlehandedly take them down with his fist, and to win his dignity as well as others respect in the process.

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his fathers death

programme.title: Reborn
programme.desc: Programmer and gamer Hao Ming gets approached by mercenary Fei Qiao and businessman Takeshi, and is drawn into a shady hacking game in Malaysia. The cyber mission quickly turns dangerous as Hao Ming must navigate the hidden motives and dealings of the mercenaries and figure out who's behind it all.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: A Murder Erased
programme.desc: Police officer Choi is assigned to a death scene investigation where the deceased body had laid undiscovered for eight years. A prosecutor joins the investigation after Choi has identified the suspect, and finds Chois actions suspicious when all manner of inconsistencies come to light from his statement...

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: Mr McDreamy
programme.desc: A second generation rich man squanders his parents money and calls himself Mr McDreamy. When his parents finally have enough and cut him off financially, he establishes a Mr McDreamy Training Academy using various unconventional means to transform his four recruits into Mr McDreamies with hilarious results.

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: Love After Love
programme.desc: Directed by Ann Hui, the movie is adapted from Eileen Changs first short story. Set in 1930s, Wei Long travels to Hong Kong from Shanghai to pursue her education. Struggling financially, she asks her aunt to help pay for tuition but ends up being her aunts puppet to lure rich men. When Wei Long falls for playboy, George, she sinks into a life of depravity.

programme.title: Eternal Wave
programme.desc: Lin Xiang is a spy trying to rebuild an underground informant network in Shanghai after the Japanese Occupation. He meets a simple but righteous girl who acts as his wife in the secret mission. When Lin is captured after his identity was revealed, his wife comes to save him but can they escape from the foes?

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard (Nick Cheung) but suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Born to Fly
programme.desc: Lei Yu has officially become the new generation of Chinese test pilots after rounds of strict selection. Captain Zhang Ting leads Lei Yu and other pilots to test the latest fighter jets. Lei Yu keeps pushing the limits in each test flight in the hope of coming up with the perfect plane to ensure the safety of the fighter pilots.

programme.title: Hail the Judge
programme.desc: A low level magistrate is run out of town for defending a beautiful murder suspect. Through a series of comedic events he ascends to the top rank & returns looking for revenge.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: The Butterfly Chalice
programme.desc: Starring the stunning, teenage heartthrob Pat Ting Hung, The Butterfly Chalice marks the important directing debut of the kung-fu film genre's most principle figure Chang Cheh, as he burst the martial arts and swordplay movie doors wide open, announcing the beginning of the end for the Cantonese musicals.

programme.title: Journey Of The Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: Golden Swallow
programme.desc: A heroine finds herself in a love triangle with a swordsman and a warrior. They team up to conquer the evil forces of the martial arts world but she is unable to choose between both men even as they face a deadly duel.

programme.title: The Big Sting
programme.desc: Three buddies find a rare artifact known as the Double-Faced God but are poisoned by Lady Wu who steals the treasure from them. Before they die, they get their wives to promise to train their children to take back what is rightfully theirs. These kids grow up to exact a vengeance that turns out to be more hilarious than horrific in this comedy.

programme.title: Legendary Weapons Of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, the leader of the Boxer Clan in Yunnan, dissolves the clan to save his disciples before going into self-exile. The Clan sends various assassins to kill him but failed. They then assigned Kungs brother Yong to find and kill Kung, leading to a battle between the two brothers.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by Drunken Master, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: The Jade Raksha
programme.desc: A fearsome swordswoman known as The Jade Raksha appears in the martial arts world and begins killing people whose surname is Yan. A swordsman figures out who she is and asks her why. Apparently a Yan killed her family 18 years ago and she only has vengeance on her mind

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Ode To Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: Holy Flame Of The Martial World
programme.desc: This internationally popular tale of a brother and sister, seeking vengeance for the death of their parents through using the mythical yin/yang Holy Flame kung-fu technique. It's an outstanding epic choreographed and co-starring lead "Venom" Kuo Chue (aka. Philip Kwok).

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Challenge Of The Masters
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung must prove himself worthy to be taught by Master Lu, who was also his fathers martial arts teacher. Although he is defeated in a competition, Wong Fei Hungs passion in Kung Fu finally moves Lu and allows him to become Lus disciple.

programme.title: Love Parade
programme.desc: Fashion designer Shi asks his friend Mui to comment on his new design but is angered by her criticism. When Mui asks him to design a gown for her to attend a gala event, Shi takes revenge by making a clown costume instead. Seeing Muis embarrassment, Shi feels guilty and apologizes to her, before they fall in love

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Huis husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and cause her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.title: The Wandering Swordsman
programme.desc: The wandering swordsman Yu Hsieh Erh has formidable sword skills and helps the poor by robbing from thieves and distributing the wealth. He meets a group of bandits who are planning to rob a convoy escorting some valuables and is tricked into participating in the robbery. Yu soon realizes his folly and returns to take revenge on the bandits.

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: Swift Sword
programme.desc: A righteous swordsman, Bai Yi Pang, seeks revenge on an evil clan but is crippled after being beaten up by them. Years later, a young man encounters Bai who is hiding in a cave. Bai decides to teach this determined young man his Swift Sword skills so that he can help Bai take revenge on the evil clan.

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: New Tales Of The Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: Tales Of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: Lady Of The Law
programme.desc: Chan, the chief of Wan Sheng Escort, is forced to raise his opponents son, Yim. While Chan forbids Yim to practice martial arts, Yim secretly learns it. Ten years later, a rapist appears and Yim is arrested by a lady constable as the suspect. The rapist turns out to be Chans elder son and Yim is framed by the Chans. Can Yim prove his innocence?

programme.title: Return Of The Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: The Treasure Hunters
programme.desc: Fans of the international star Alexander Fu Sheng were aghast. Their idol had broken both his legs and was recuperating. Everyone wondered: would he be able to return to the action comedies for which he was so famous? This movie was the answer, and it left no doubt that he had made a full recovery. Liu Chia-yung, brother of preeminent martial arts moviemaker Liu Chia-liang, was famous in his own right for kung-fu comedies, and he out-did himself with this one. Imagine Bob Hope and Bing Crosby with the skills of Jet Li and Jackie Chan, and youve got an idea of the fun and fury inherent in this delightful tale of two con men vying for a horde of hidden gold. Add to the mix a Shaolin monk (played by "Master Killer" Gordon Liu Chia-hui), a powerfully brutal villain, and his equally dangerous mute sister (future director Yang Tsing-tsing), and youve got one of the most internationally loved kung-fu capers ever made.
